data.description: Seller’s are building new home and have reduced price well below market value to ensure a quick sale. This home is located in the highly desired Stonechase Community and is quite possibly situated on the very best lot within the neighborhood. Great curb appeal, fenced in rear yard with amazing heated pool and great views of pond. This 3 bedroom home has a large loft that can be easily/economically converted to a 4th bedroom if desired. The main floor offers a super spacious open floor plan with a large kitchen equipped with an island, loads of cabinets, and countertop space, lots of windows allowing endless natural light, as well as office area, dining, sunroom, etc. New roof in 2023, new upstairs carpet, possession at closing. A quote for converting the loft to 4th bedroom can be provided.
